						"description":"**Holographic Edge Glow**\r\n\r\n*A striking emissive effect that highlights edges with a neon glow.*  \r\n\r\n- Perfect for holograms, sci-fi props, or UI elements  \r\n- Fully procedural with adjustable glow intensity and color  \r\n- Enhances futuristic and digital aesthetics with ease  \r\n- Works beautifully in both dark and high-contrast scenes  \r\n\r\nIf this glow effect fits your work, leaving a rating would really support me as a designer.",
